  "title": "Sales Promoter",
  "description": "<p>📍<strong> Island-wide locations</strong><br />⏰ Min. 8-10 hrs shift per day <em><strong>(Schedule based on roster)</strong></em><br />📅 5-6 days work week<br />💰 Up to $3,000/month<br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u><br />• Proactively approach, greet and engage customers in a warm, friendly and professional manner to promote new product launches, seasonal items and ongoing promotions.<br />• Perform up-selling and cross-selling to maximize sales value while maintaining a positive and enjoyable customer experience.<br />• Create, arrange and maintain visually appealing product displays that highlight best-sellers, new launches and promotional items to attract customers' attention.<br />• Ensure all promotional materials, including signage, price tags and display labels are accurately displayed and kept up to date at all times.<br />• Work closely with outlet staff to support daily sales targets, ensure smooth operations and contribute to a positive and collaborative team environment.<br />• Collect and share customers' feedback, market trends and competitors' insights with management to support continuous improvement in products, promotions and sales strategies.<br />• Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned by the Supervisor/ Manager to ensure efficient and effective outlet operations. <br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u><br />• <strong>Singaporeans Only</strong><br />• Min. 1-2 years of relevant experience as a Sales Promoter/ Brand Ambassador/ Customer Service role is an advantage.<br />• Outgoing, confident and energetic personality with genuine passion for customers.<br />• Strong communication and interpersonal skills, with the ability to influence and persuade customers. <br />• Responsible, reliable and team-oriented with the ability to perform well in a fast-paced environment.<br />• Willingness to travel across different Four Leaves outlets within the assigned region as required. <br /></p><p><u><strong>Staffs' Benefits:</strong></u><br />• Annual & Medical leaves entitlement<br />• Medical claims<br />• AWS/ VB<br />• Annual salary increment <em><strong>(based on individuals' work performance)</strong></em><br /><em><strong></strong></em></p><p>📱 Interested applicants, can<strong> WhatsApp @ 84944246</strong> OR <strong>Tele: @fourleaveshr</strong></p>",
