    "description": "<p>Established since 1981, Four Leaves has developed into one of the leading chain bakery in Singapore and have since successfully launched our central factory located at Enterprise Road and 28 retail outlets in Singapore.</p>    <p> </p>    <p>Besides the core brand of Four Leaves, we are also managing the brand names of St. Leaven (Takashimaya), Peck (Takashimaya), Epid’or (Raffles City) and Splash n Decker (Ngee Ann Polytechnic). In addition, we also have two subsidiaries in Kuala Lumpur and Penang of Malaysia.</p>  ",
